ize the mac and cheese for easy transfer to the oven and even cooking.\u003c/p\u003e","equipment":["8\" medium pot","10\" medium high-sided pan","baking sheet"],"id":7089,"ingredients":["fresh mozzarella","yellow onion","mini penne","unsalted butter","flour","milk","shredded mozzarella and provolone","pesto","shaved Parmesan cheese","basil","grape tomatoes","aluminum tin"],"ingredients_full":[{"name":"fresh mozzarella","quantity":"4.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1093/medium_square_fresh_mozzarella.jpg"},{"name":"yellow onion","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":2,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/27/medium_square_yellow-onion-test.jpg"},{"name":"mini penne","quantity":"8.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":3,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2363/medium_square_penne-pasta_copy.jpg"},{"name":"unsalted butter","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"packet","displayOrder":4,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2371/medium_square_medium_square_butter-test.jpg"},{"name":"flour","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":5,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/285/medium_square_FLOUR_copy.jpg"},{"name":"milk","quantity":"8.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":6,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/129/medium_square_coconut-milk.jpg"},{"name":"shredded mozzarella and provolone","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":7,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2304/medium_square_2017-02-09___DS_17130281.jpg"},{"name":"pesto","quantity":"0.25","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":8,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1075/medium_square_PESTO_-4396_copy.jpg"},{"name":"shaved Parmesan cheese","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":9,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2328/medium_square_SHAVED_PARM.jpg"},{"name":"basil","quantity":"0.125","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":10,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/5/medium_square_basil-test.jpg"},{"name":"grape tomatoes","quantity":"0.25","measurementUnit":"pint","displayOrder":11,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/191/medium_square_GRAPE_TOMATOES_copy.jpg"},{"name":"aluminum tin","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":12,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/830/medium_square_square_baking_tin.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":["olive oil","kosher salt","black pepper"],"pantry_items_full":[{"name":"olive oil","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":null,"displayOrder":13,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/267/medium_square_olive-oil-test.jpg"},{"name":"kosher salt","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":14,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/473/medium_square_kosher-salt.jpg"},{"name":"black pepper","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":15,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/493/medium_square_spice-black-pepper-test.jpg"}],"steps":[{"title":"Prepare ingredients","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/69443/recipe_card_size_dLKpdItcSi5meCOsvlHU_1._Prepare_Ingredients.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003ePreheat oven to 450°F. Bring a medium pot of water to a boil over high heat. Rinse all produce. Thinly slice \u003cstrong\u003efresh\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003emozzarella\u003c/strong\u003e. Peel \u003cstrong\u003eonion\u003c/strong\u003e and cut into small dice.  \u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Boil penne and sauté onion","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/69445/recipe_card_size_tQHEKCQaWFXOQFPLVlVg_2._Boil_Penne_and_Saute_Onion.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eSeason boiling water generously with \u003cstrong\u003esalt\u003c/strong\u003e. Stir in \u003cstrong\u003emini penne\u003c/strong\u003e and cook until al dente, about 7 minutes. Reserve \u003cstrong\u003e.5 cup pasta cooking water\u003c/strong\u003e, then drain and return to pot, off heat. Meanwhile, heat \u003cstrong\u003ebutter\u003c/strong\u003e in a medium high-sided pan over medium-high heat. When butter is foamy, add \u003cstrong\u003eonion\u003c/strong\u003e; sauté, stirring, until softened, 2-3 minutes. \u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Make cheese sauce","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/69444/recipe_card_size_jj8yMtRLyIAd7wWA6LDg_3._Make_Cheese_Sauce.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eReduce heat under pan to medium and add \u003cstrong\u003eflour\u003c/strong\u003e; cook, stirring, until flour is lightly browned, 1 minute. Whisking constantly, add \u003cstrong\u003emilk\u003c/strong\u003e and cook until thickened, 2-3 minutes more. Remove pan from heat. Stir in \u003cstrong\u003eshredded mozzarella and provolone\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003epesto\u003c/strong\u003e,\u003cstrong\u003e half of Parmesan\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e.25 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e, and\u003cstrong\u003e pepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired to combine.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Assemble mac and cheese","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/69446/recipe_card_size_6Y9ArMX8S1eooS0M0ALS_4._Assemble_Mac_and_Cheese_2X.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eOnce cooked and drained, add \u003cstrong\u003emini penne \u003c/strong\u003eto pan with cheese sauce, still off heat, and toss to coat. Adding 1 tablespoon at a time, stir in \u003cstrong\u003ereserved pasta cooking water\u003c/strong\u003e until sauce is silky and clings to noodles (see recipe tip). Reshape \u003cstrong\u003ealuminum tin\u003c/strong\u003e, if bent, then pour in \u003cstrong\u003emac and cheese\u003c/strong\u003e and spread in an even layer. Place \u003cstrong\u003etin\u003c/strong\u003e on a baking sheet (see recipe tip). Top with \u003cstrong\u003esliced mozzarella\u003c/strong\u003e in a single layer.\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Bake mac and cheese","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/69447/recipe_card_size_soIK1iOiQFKeU7JiNItP_5._Bake_Mac_and_Cheese_2X.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eBake \u003cstrong\u003emac and cheese\u003c/strong\u003e until cheese is melted and bubbling, 14-16 minutes. Meanwhile, roughly tear \u003cstrong\u003ebasil\u003c/strong\u003e leaves, discarding stems. Quarter \u003cstrong\u003egrape\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003etomatoes\u003c/strong\u003e; place in a medium bowl with \u003cstrong\u003e1 tablespoon olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e,\u003cstrong\u003e .125\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eteaspoon\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003esalt\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired and toss to coat. \u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Plate mac and cheese","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/69448/recipe_card_size_lPyC9yG0T0GUIUkvvM8A_6._Plate.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eDivide \u003cstrong\u003eCaprese\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003emac and cheese\u003c/strong\u003e between serving bowls. Top with \u003cstrong\u003ebasil\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003egrape tomatoes\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003eremaining Parmesan\u003c/strong\u003e. Dig in!\u003c/p\u003e"}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Family-friendly","slug":"family-friendly","hex_color":""}],"allergens":[{"name":"Milk","slug":"milk","hex_color":""},{